AC6: go test ./internal/connect/... 所有子包可加载

--- Step 1: 子包结构 ---
connect/
  user/         (2 files)  auth_handler.go, account_handler.go
  admin/        (7 files)  admin_{account,config,jurisdiction,log,system,trading,user}_handler.go
  ai/           (4 files)  ai_handler.go, ai_primary_handler.go, code_assist_handler.go, system_ai_handler.go
  strategy/     (5 files)  strategy_handler.go, strategy_asset_handler.go, strategy_experiment_handler.go, python_strategy_handler.go, backtest_trades_handler.go
  marketplace/  (4 files)  marketplace_handler.go, market_handler.go, market_regime_handler.go, indicator_catalog_handler.go
  system/       (7 files)  stream_handler.go, job_handler.go, log_handler.go, schedule_health_handler.go, mthub_service.go, economic_data_handler.go, analytics_handler.go

Total: 29 files in 6 subpackages.

--- Step 2: Package 声明 ---
All 29 files updated from "package connect" to respective subpackage names:
  user → package user
  admin → package admin
  ai → package ai
  strategy → package strategy
  marketplace → package marketplace
  system → package system

--- Step 3: main.go import 修复 ---
Old (single flat import):
  "anttrader/internal/connect"

New (6 subpackage imports):
  "anttrader/internal/connect/admin"
  "anttrader/internal/connect/ai"
  mktplace "anttrader/internal/connect/marketplace"  // aliased: conflicts with internal/marketplace
  "anttrader/internal/connect/strategy"
  "anttrader/internal/connect/system"
  "anttrader/internal/connect/user"

Alias required: "anttrader/internal/connect/marketplace" package name is "marketplace",
which conflicts with existing import "anttrader/internal/marketplace" (service layer).
Resolved with: mktplace "anttrader/internal/connect/marketplace"

